---Register a function to be run when mod configuration changes. This is called when the game version or any mod version changes; when any mod is added or removed; or when prototypes or startup mod settings have changed. It allows the mod to make any changes it deems appropriate to both the data structures in its `global` table or to the game state through [LuaGameScript](https://lua-api.factorio.com/latest/LuaGameScript.html).
---
---[View documentation](https://lua-api.factorio.com/latest/LuaBootstrap.html#LuaBootstrap.on_configuration_changed)
